Representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths, while career counselors remind attendees to maintain eye contact. Inside, a whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews. As the event progresses, announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair, and a startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session. Before the fair opens, students line up outside the gym.

A whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews, and career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops. Healthcare providers showcase community outreach photos at the event. Announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair, and a post-event survey link flashes on the monitors near the exit. Additionally, workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom.

A welcome announcement outlines the fair schedule over the PA system. Interview sign-up sheets fill with names, reflecting the interest in potential opportunities as career counselors redirect unsure students toward applicable industries, reminding attendees to maintain eye contact during interactions. Meanwhile, career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops. As the fair progresses, announcement chimes signal the final hour of the event.
